" Option Settings {{{
set nocompatible " Necesary for lots of cool vim things
set tabstop=4
set shiftwidth=4
set shiftround
set expandtab
set smarttab
set textwidth=79
set number
set ignorecase
set smartcase
set autoindent
set incsearch
set autoread "Automatically load external changes to file
